### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### Health check
# @name health
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### Create user (unique email to avoid duplicates)
# @name createUser
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/usuarios
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "João Silva",
  "email": "joao+{{$timestamp}}@email.com",
  "senha": "senha123",
  "cargo": "Aluno"
}

### List users
# @name listUsers
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/usuarios

### Create class (turma) using created user as admin
# @name createTurma
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/turmas
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Engenharia de Software",
  "descricao": "Turma de ES 2024",
  "tipo": "classe",
  "publico": true,
  "administradorId": {{createUser.response.body.id}}
}

### List classes (turmas)
# @name listTurmas
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/turmas

### Create event using created turma
# @name createEvento
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/eventos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "titulo": "Aula de Banco de Dados {{$timestamp}}",
  "descricao": "Introdução ao MySQL",
  "dataInicio": "2025-11-25T14:00:00",
  "dataFim": "2025-11-25T16:00:00",
  "local": "Sala 101",
  "publico": false,
  "turmaId": {{createTurma.response.body.id}}
}

### List events
# @name listEventos
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/eventos
